import React from 'react'; import Navbar from './Navbar'; function AboutPage() { return (

About Westland Properties

Westland Properties is a leading real estate company dedicated to providing exceptional service and unparalleled market knowledge. Our team of experienced agents is committed to helping you find your dream home or investment property.

Our Mission

At Westland Properties, our mission is to provide a personalized and professional approach to buying and selling real estate. We strive to build long-term relationships with our clients and provide them with the highest level of service and expertise.

Our Team

  • John Doe, Broker
  • Jane Smith, Agent
  • Bob Johnson, Agent

© 2024 Westland Properties

); } export default AboutPage;
